        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="piktogram piktogram--hidden">
      <div class="piktogram__box">
        <div class="piktogram__circle">
          <img src="./images/symbols/29mm.svg" alt="29mm" height="75px" loading="lazy" />
          <small>29 mm</small>
        </div>
        <div class="piktogram__circle">
          <img src="./images/symbols/29mm.svg" alt="29mm" height="75px" loading="lazy" />
          <small>29 mm</small>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="piktogram__desc">
        <p class="desc">
          <span>Oblíbená verze o síle 29mm, obsahující </span>
